14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1698.501 of Title 69, unless
17 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 The bridge on U.S. Highway 70 crossing over Winters Creek
19 approximately three (3) miles northeast of Bennington in Bryan
20 County shall be designated as the "Clyde and Grace Cook Memorial
21 Bridge". The Department of Transportation shall cause suitable
22 permanent markers bearing that name to be placed on the bridge.
